The Frjosa Hel-vegr River~
   You are underneath the waterfall that feeds the Frjosa Hel-Vegr River.  
Freezing water and ice is crashing down all around you, making visibility low.
The sound is near deafening.  The current is pushing you eastwards.  There is
something strange behind the waterfall that could be worth investigating.  
