#31851
Underneath the Bridge of Frjosa Hel-vegr~
   Above you is the bridge's &cfrozen&n underbelly.  Northward the vital artery of
the north spans across a raging torrent of freezing water and sludge.  It's
construction is of god-like quality.  There are no visible joints, and is
entirely made from some sort of dull black stone.  There is a small, extremely
primitive campsite tucked up and dug in to the south where the bridge meets
this god-forsaken tundra.  East will bring you out from underneath the bridge
and back into the frey.  
~
