#31854
The Frjosa Hel-vegr Tundra~
   You are where the tundra and the taiga meet.  The last bit of vegetation is
scattered to the south and the hateful, unforgiving, frozen wasteland to the
north.  The air is devoid of moisture as anything of that nature is solidified
by the frigid temperatures.  The wind is strong and blows hard from several
directions.  
~
318 0 0 0 0 0
D0
   You may jump into the river from this direction, however you will not be
able to come back up.  There is a long drop to the river and it is frozen
sheer cliff on either side of it.  
~
~
