#31855
Behind the Great Falls of Frjosa Hel-vgr River~
   You are in a large hidden cavern behind the falls.  The smell of fish and
dead flesh overwhelms you.  There is a very large pile of bones, destroyed
armors, and debris to the south.  To the west wall of the cavern you see a
large pool of glistening blue water.  Around this pool blood stained rock and
ice catch your attention.  On the west wall, something has been carved.  
~
318 12 0 0 0 0
D1
~
secret~
0 -1 31800
E
carving carved stone wall~
From below the dragon

dark comes forth,

Nidhoggr flying

from Nithafjoll 

The bodies of men

on his wings he bears,

